sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import { Button, Container } from '../../GlobalStyles' import { InfoSect, InfoRow, InfoColumn, TextWrapper, TopLine, Heading, SubTitle, ImgWrapper, Img } from './InfoSection.elements' import img from "../../images/info1.png" import WarningRoundedIcon from '@material-ui/icons/WarningRounded'; const InfoSection = ({ primary, lightBg, imgStart, lightTextDesc, lightTopline, buttonLabel, description, headLine, lightText, topLine, start, alt }) => { return ( <> {topLine} {headLine} {description} ) } export default InfoSection
